{"tid":1438750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲點黎？藍 報 橫 行 !","createTime":"2019-08-10T01:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T01:57:18.000Z","uid":92836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"056bd283cfa1c44f35eb9467cda71d2e32d6fff0","tid":1438750,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:01:41.000Z","msg":"頭條日報呢類免費報紙<br />\n會出現係大量私人屋苑及黨鐵鐵站<br />\n如果有手足可以幫手攞曬去回收<br />\n就可以斷絕呢類藍報橫行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果可以我哋都可以整一份報紙出嚟<br />\n 同港共政府搏鬥 加上大量文宣<br />\n制衡免費藍報</span></span><br />\n<br />\n長期下去意形態就會對立， 繼而有社會上所講嘅藍絲出現， 因為長期接收錯誤扭曲嘅資訊。<br />\n佢哋會好討厭抗議或反對嘅一切行為<br />\n甚至進化到佢哋會認為遊行冇問題但要和平<br />\n<br />\n有冇更好嘅對策？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1bkgSKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1bkgSKs.jpg&h=01dc0350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D1ZtJRa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD1ZtJRa.jpg&h=868e3538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eUsCCbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeUsCCbd.jpg&h=06a246d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OPYmCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OPYmCY.jpg&h=d27255b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b372e63fc7270d441c281323d513f50cac9cb315","tid":1438750,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:04:44.000Z","msg":"免費報紙問題係錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推行動post呀！<br />\n<br />\n【置頂+廣傳】８.１０ 大 埔 逃 生 路 線 圖 （附 廣 場 名）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d516671d289ab1082b97025e52839c1eec4d767f","tid":1438750,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b372e63fc7270d441c281323d513f50cac9cb315","tid":1438750,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci